<section class="section" style="padding-top:calc(var(--gap) + 80px);background:linear-gradient(170deg,var(--white) 0%,var(--secondary-ultra-light) 35%,var(--primary-ultra-light) 65%,var(--secondary-ultra-light) 100%)">
  <div class="blob" style="width:500px;height:500px;top:-100px;right:-100px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,171,189,.07),transparent 60%)"></div>
  <div class="blob" style="width:400px;height:400px;bottom:-80px;left:-80px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(224,113,44,.05),transparent 60%)"></div>
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="feature-split">
      <div class="feat-text">
        <span class="script script-hero" style="color:var(--accent)">Get Back to What Matters</span>
        <h1 class="headline" style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)">You opened your center <span style="color:var(--secondary-text)">to change kids' lives.</span><br>Not to drown in busy work.</h1>
        <p class="subhead">Paper sign-in sheets, texting parents from your personal phone, student data scattered across five different apps, no real-time view of your classroom. It all pulled you away from the reason you started. The Center Book handles center operations so your staff gets back to what matters most: the students.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap"><a href="#" class="btn btn-founding" data-cta="Become a Founding Center">Become a Founding Center</a><a href="#" class="btn btn-demo" data-cta="Book a Demo">Book a Demo</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-visual">
        <div class="blob" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(53,92,170,.06),rgba(0,171,189,.06));width:120%;height:120%;top:-10%;left:-10%"></div>
        <div class="shot"><img src="/images/img-01.png" alt="The Center Book attendance board"></div>
        <div class="float-el" style="bottom:24px;left:-20px;border-left:3px solid var(--secondary-text)"><i data-lucide="send" style="width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--secondary-text)"></i> <span><strong style="color:var(--primary)">Text sent to parent</strong><br>"Ariella is ready for pickup."</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

